{"tid":1920210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Sharp對支企 咸陽彩虹光電、冠捷科技與 Vizio 等提出液晶技術侵權訴訟","createTime":"2020-03-11T10:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T16:06:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18f4e5f5a564ef84d14628722a041d4916541883","tid":1920210,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"Chevelle.fu<br />\n<br />\n夏普 Sharp 先前針對 OPPO 與日本 OPPO 就 LTE 通訊技術提起侵權訴訟，而最近又把矛頭指向面板與電視廠商，對中國的咸陽彩虹光電 CHOT 、冠捷 TPV 與 Vizio 等提出液晶技術侵權，指出這幾家廠商恐侵犯夏普達 12 項專利，夏普已經在美國時間 3 月 10 日向美國加州中部法院提出專利訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n根據夏普的說法，這些專利涉及 PSA 技術與 HD 面板技術，同時夏普已經自 2019 年 11 月持續向 CHOT 提出專利侵權的情形，同時亦與 CHOT 設法進行溝通談判與提出證據，不過 CHOT 仍未理會，夏普決定發動專利訴訟，針對 CHOT 在未經授權之下使用夏普專利造成的損失提出訴訟禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/152362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F152362&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stsWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=55f3643d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/152362</a>"},{"pid":"955d8e37430151e3676177d3ca7a759600396864","tid":1920210,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d06e16ce243775a46aa1679e7a8e08af8889515","tid":1920210,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"支那狗日日抄人"},{"pid":"786dde27f3f80f6a81bc806edcb24b2a8e5e1432","tid":1920210,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"新業務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7b9a8466e9b61f3e1d66079c5d32acfa3c3a9d","tid":1920210,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:53:28.000Z","msg":"Sharp 俾台灣郭台銘收購左，而家係台灣公司"},{"pid":"1f395766e01849e4c76c1cfff9e233b72d18f4cd","tid":1920210,"uid":48083,"li